Overview

Charming Renovated 3-Bed/ 2-Bath Brick Ranch in Merewood! Step into this beautifully renovated brick ranch, nestled in the desirable Merewood community. With 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, this home is the perfect blend of modern updates and classic charm. Newer LVP flooring and abundant natural light create a welcoming ambiance throughout the spacious living areas. The expansive kitchen features elegant white cabinetry, newer countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a stylish subway tile backsplash. A barn-style door leads to a second living/family/rec. space--a thoughtful addition to the original home--perfect for entertaining and relaxation. Adjacent to the added living space is a screened-in back porch, overlooking a meticulously landscaped backyard, complete with lush flowerbeds, and the fully fenced-in yard gives you plenty of privacy. A detached two-car garage, complete with a new roof and opener, offers plenty of storage and work space. The home also boasts a new HVAC system, gutters, and downspouts on both house and garage. Added improvements include six new windows, new front and back Champion doors, full attic insulation and updated plumbing. Don't miss your opportunity to
